Author: jesselivermore
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🌎 TOKENBOX 🌎 - Ecosystem for crypto investors, funds and traders
Body: Tokenbox co-founder and managing partner to speak at Global Blockchain Summit in Sochi    This weekend a beautiful city of Sochi will host the Global Blockchain Summit 2018 (https://mania.events/en/), an exciting conference and exhibition event devoted to everything crypto. The summit is set for March 24th, and will gather entrepreneurs, developers, blockchain bosses, crypto enthusiasts, analysts, head of IT and development departments etc. Attendees will discuss such matters as problems while holding an ICO, Bitcoin price range in 2018, the most efficient ways of investing in crypto and of course the future of blockchain. There are some key names among the speakers of the summit: Qu Wenbo, Professor of Shanghai Business School; Juwan Lee, CEO NexChange; Samson Lee, Co-founder of Hong Kong Blockchain Centre; Yan Lin, Overseas Development Manager Huobi. Heads of various Russian and international blockchain startups will also speak during the programme. Tokenbox will be represented by Viktor Shpakovsky, who will speak on how to create and manage a cryptocurrency portfolio. Looking forward to see you at Rosa Hutor, home for the Global blockchain summit amidst the beautiful mountains and once the home for the Winter Olympics!  Check out Tokenbox Blog for News and Updates https://medium.com/tokenbox

Author: jesselivermore
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🌎 TOKENBOX 🌎 - Ecosystem for crypto investors, funds and traders
Body: Tokenbox partners with FINTECH Russia, CEO Pavel Salas to host the event    March 30th is reserved for a massive fintech gathering in Moscow — FINTECH Russia 2018 (https://fintechrussia.ru). Tokenbox is one of the main partners of this conference, featuring both an exciting digital workshop and an exhibition. We are pleased to announce our Chief Executive, Pavel Salas, as an honored moderator of the event. FINTECH Russia, founded in 2014, is aimed to develop a brand new approach to the whole fintech ecosystem, which currently only describes changes of the present, not answering challenging questions posed by the future. During the program both digital modernization and digital transformation will be thoroughly analyzed by considering various cases and scenarios. There will be presenters from different fields, from AI implementing to banking sectors, telling their stories and discussing challenges made by digital era to business and society. See you on March 30th at Technopolis Moscow, the smartest city hub for hi-tech industries!  Check out Tokenbox Blog for News and Updates https://medium.com/tokenbox

Author: jesselivermore
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🌎 TOKENBOX 🌎 - Ecosystem for crypto investors, funds and traders
Body: RACIB & Tokenbox to hold an ICO pitch session at BLOCKCHAINRF-2018    BLOCKCHAINRF-2018 is the biggest industry gathering for developers and users of blockchain based products. On the first day of the congress, March 27th, a powerful session will take place at the venue. Industry’s newest and coolest projects will be presented in front of potential investors. The pitch-session is organized by RACIB (Russian Association of Cryptocurrencies and Blockchain) in partnership with Tokenbox. Teams from China, Germany, USA, Russia and Ukraine will tell about their brand new digital projects and present fresh ideas of blockchain technology implementation. A panel of experts will assess the prospects of the projects, which are going to launch an ICO soon. The experts are: Victor Goncharuk, Vice President of RACIB, Vladimir Smerkis — Tokenbox co-founder and managing partner, Viktor Shpakovsky — The Token Fund co-founder, Alexey Markov, United Traders leading trader, Ilya Etko — digital business and innovation partner at Deloitte CIS, Mikhail Mashchenko — head of analytical department at eToro, and others. Tokenbox and RACIB are pleased to invite investors to support the ICOs development, to shape the future of digital economy and take part in the pitch-session. Follow the link to fill in the application form: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfRAar_e53xfhHFRsZJi30eccxMmUc8dHVhMT4_vxNeE4t4qw/viewform?usp=sf_link

Author: jesselivermore
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🌎 TOKENBOX 🌎 - Ecosystem for crypto investors, funds and traders
Body: Viktor Shpakovsky, Tokenbox co-founder and managing partner, rocking the stage Global Blockchain Summit 2018 in Sochi, Russia. Viktor and the whole Token Team are very happy and grateful to be a part of the Summit’s eventful program. Apart from meeting so many interesting people from the industry and sharing views on the whole blockchain and digital economy future, Viktor had amazing company while celebrating The Token Fund 1 year anniversary, which was March 24th! Yay!

Title: [ANN][ICO] 🌎 TOKENBOX 🌎 - Ecosystem for crypto investors, funds and traders
Body: _______________________________________________________________________________ ___________________________  The Token Generation Event will start on November 14th  !!!*** Whales are already here ***!!!  _______________________________________________________________________________ ___________________________    Public issue: 31 000 000 tokens  Date of issue: 14th November  How to acquire tokens: by ETH and BTC  Hard cap: 20,000,000 USD     ***********************************  Calm Down & Join the Queue  ***********************************         ####################  Read the Tokenbox White Paper  ####################                              What is Tokenbox?  ___________________________________________________________________________   With the development of blockchain technology and the rapid growth of the crypto-currency market, new opportunities appear consistently in the field of Investment.  The traditional economy changes its form, new values arise in the digital "world" and a significant role in these processes is played by decentralised technologies, in which cryptocurrencies and digital tokens play a critical role.  Increasingly, they are described as "crypto or digital assets".  Professionals of the crypto market (portfolio managers and traders) are also often not sufciently open to potential investors, as they are afraid of the influence of regulators and do not have a set of technical (software) solutions for the most efcient management of funds and interaction with their customers.  That's why we developed the Tokenbox Platform concept - a trust management ecosystem that unites investors on the one hand, and crypto-currency funds in the person of professional managers and traders on the other.        Terms Of Tokensale ___________________________________________________________________________     •  The ticker of Tokenbox's token is TBX  •  The price of a single TBX is 1 USD during all stages of TGE  •  Tokensale is consisted of two phases: Private Sale and Token Generation Event  •  The Private Sale is being arranged through advanced orders  •  Token Generation Event will commence on the 14th November, 2017  •  Token generation and delivery to its investors will be completed within 10 days of the TGE event  •  Token acquisition is set up via crypto currencies: BTC and ETH  •  Representatives of the The Token Fund and Zerion (Fund’s partner) control smart-contracts and address where cryptocurrency is collected via multi-signature  •  TBX will be further listed at the crypto exchanges and will have its market price        About TBX ___________________________________________________________________________   TBX tokens are utilised on the platform, thereby providing funds and traders with access to the Tokenbox operations as described below. This methodology for utilising a TBX token can best be attributed to several “rules”:    1. A fund or trader who wishes to operate their own fund on the platform and take advantage of all the facilities provided, acquires TBX tokens and deposits them on the platform.  2. Any fund using the platform is required to maintain 5% of all assets in its portfolio in TBX.  3. The value of all assets of the fund (including TBX) for compliance with this ratio is calculated in US dollars;  4. The value of assets in the fund's portfolio fluctuates over time as the value of market assets also fluctuates, according to the transaction volume of incoming and outgoing funds from other investors.  5. Funds can acquire TBX tokens on stock exchanges in order to meet the TBX 5% threshold.         ####################  Tokenbox.io  ####################        ########################################  We believe that today, an instrument that can ensure the efective management of private and institutional investors' assets on the market and can enable this wider market to enter this market, is a necessity.
